         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">1/6/80. ¶  ¶ I intended to call on you at Gov House, dear Dr Hector, to enjoy a talk with you after 18 years once more; ¶ Hector and M had met in early 1862 when Hector passed through Melbourne on his...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">80.06.01</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To James Hector</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">MU 94, box 4 (4440/80), Museum of New Zealand Te Papa Tongarewa Archives, Wellington.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style=""/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M's letter was registered at the Geological Survey Office, Wellington, on 21 June 1880.</p>
               </note>1/6/80.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I intended to call on you at Gov House, dear Dr Hector, to enjoy a talk with you after 18 years once more;<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Hector and M had met in early 1862 when Hector passed through Melbourne on his way to take up his initial appointment in NZ, furnished with letters of introduction to M from Joseph Hooker and J. H. Balfour; see M to J. Haast, 16 March 1862.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>but when I went you had just taken your departure for Hobarton.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Now Hobart, Tas.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>At the evening of her Majesty's Birthday<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>24 May.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I went with the Italian Consul General, who drove me up to Gov. Palace,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>so that I kept with that nobleman on the table, otherwise I would have endeavoured to get a seat near you.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It devolves yet on me to thank you for having advertised for tenders for Kauri-seeds. Meanwhile a supply reached the Melbourne Market, which I bought, so that I shall not require any more at present.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Regardfully your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
         </div>
      </body>
